1114
01:19:40,560 --> 01:19:42,819
[SPEAKER_01] A On je, On je, On jest ljubav.

1115
01:19:42,920 --> 01:19:45,300
[SPEAKER_01] Bog je ljubav, kako Ivan kaže u prvoj poslanici.

1116
01:19:45,300 --> 01:19:48,739
[SPEAKER_00] Amen.

1117
01:19:48,739 --> 01:19:49,460
[SPEAKER_01] Amen.

1118
01:19:49,460 --> 01:19:50,659
[SPEAKER_01] Aleluja.

1119
01:19:50,659 --> 01:19:54,300
[SPEAKER_00] Nemam šta dodat.

1120
01:19:54,300 --> 01:19:56,119
[SPEAKER_00] Kako bi rekli ovdje, da bi reč rekal.

1121
01:19:56,119 --> 01:20:03,199
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, ja osjećam da bismo mogli tu čak zaključiti ovaj razgovor.

1122
01:20:03,199 --> 01:20:05,720
[SPEAKER_01] Ok, bilo mi je super, ne znam koliko dugo sjedim.

1123
01:20:05,720 --> 01:20:09,680
[SPEAKER_00] Puno toga smo rekli, mogli bismo još sad još ja, mislim, satima,

1124
01:20:09,680 --> 01:20:11,720
