1125
01:20:11,720 --> 01:20:12,800
[SPEAKER_01] Pa evo.

1126
01:20:12,800 --> 01:20:15,720
[SPEAKER_00] Jesmo li nešto zaboravili bitno što se čini?

1127
01:20:15,720 --> 01:20:16,319
